---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | StockTheEvent"
  description="Privacy policy for StockTheEvent drink calculator. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-b from-amber-50 to-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mb-8">Last updated: January 1, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          StockTheEvent is committed to protecting your privacy. We collect minimal information to provide our services:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Email Address:</strong> Only if you voluntarily subscribe to receive your shopping list or planning tips.</li>
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Anonymous analytics about how visitors use our calculators (page views, calculator usage).</li>
          <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> We use essential cookies for site functionality and analytics cookies to improve our service.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>To send you the shopping list you requested</li>
          <li>To send occasional party planning tips (if subscribed)</li>
          <li>To improve our calculators and user experience</li>
          <li>To analyze site traffic and usage patterns</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Information Sharing</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties. We may share anonymous, aggregated data for analytics purposes.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          Our site contains links to Amazon and other retailers through affiliate programs. These sites have their own privacy policies, and we encourage you to review them. We earn a small commission from qualifying purchases at no extra cost to you.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Data Security</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          You have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-slate-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Unsubscribe from our emails at any time</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your email from our records</li>
          <li>Access information we have about you</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          Our service is not intended for individuals under the legal drinking age. We do not knowingly collect information from minors.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-700 mb-4">
          If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us through our website.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
